{"tid":813311,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"港足新帥霸氣回應批評: 「我們不會去理會任何亂吠的野狗！」","createTime":"2018-09-10T10:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T08:39:56.000Z","uid":9030,"like":85,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"cc4e543dc16c0469f80a0fcd8309ca0b748ae3d6","tid":813311,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T10:53:02.000Z","msg":"韋特在台灣執教時，評論對他毁譽參半，而這位港隊新帥未及上任，在香港亦已引起各界熱烈討論，他坦言不會理會外間言論：「就像任何一個國家隊教練，我覺得自己就像一頭獅子，作為獅子，我們不會去理會任何亂吠的野狗，前方還有更多更重要的事要做，無論你去哪裹，總有人對你有意見，例如造謠生事，這也是我工作的一部份，我只會集中去贏波，領軍登上新的高度。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/185242_c5183151155d2a90dce5fe365b0d5b0e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F185242_c5183151155d2a90dce5fe365b0d5b0e.png&h=c3dc33dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f8c67a9ee37fedab694b7ca2a02dd24b4491535","tid":813311,"uid":78873,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T11:00:37.000Z","msg":"DAY One就戰鬥格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留得幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9595de46f25fb49b43012862acd1b4c603e59cb","tid":813311,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"4f8c67a9ee37fedab694b7ca2a02dd24b4491535","tid":813311,"uid":78873,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T11:00:37.000Z","msg":"DAY One就戰鬥格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留得幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T11:08:54.000Z","msg":"要睇睇"},{"pid":"2f4117cf8699f5aeba935ddf6b370e313dda04f2","tid":813311,"uid":78873,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"e9595de46f25fb49b43012862acd1b4c603e59cb","tid":813311,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"4f8c67a9ee37fedab694b7ca2a02dd24b4491535","tid":813311,"uid":78873,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"rep